Subtask 1.2: Basic DNS Resolution with DNSx
Let's start with basic DNS resolution to understand how DNSx works.

# Create a working directory for this lab
mkdir ~/lab3-dns-mapping
cd ~/lab3-dns-mapping

# Create a sample domain list
cat > domains.txt << EOF
google.com
github.com
stackoverflow.com
cloudflare.com
