Subtask 1.3: Advanced DNS Enumeration
Now let's perform more comprehensive DNS enumeration to gather additional information.

# Perform comprehensive DNS enumeration
dnsx -l domains.txt -a -aaaa -cname -mx -ns -txt -resp -o comprehensive_dns.txt

